    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "dissolve into the background? what does that even mean... you mean like just letting go and not caring anymore? it feels like there's no point in trying to be seen when nobody's even looking. it's like i'm already gone, and the only thing left is the effort of pretending i'm here.",
